{"tid":1975854,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打隻狗試過咁","createTime":"2020-04-16T23:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T06:57:32.000Z","uid":163654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc9da8207f090316fbce519877dc18f54a7fd0b","tid":1975854,"uid":163654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:05:39.000Z","msg":"我有一隻11歲嘅貴婦狗  佢尼兩日冇啦啦勁痴人  但係條尾就收起左(姐係d狗唔開心 唔舒服果隻收尾)  <br />\n<br />\n又抖晒大氣咁(狗仔夏天天氣熱申晒脷果隻) <br />\n開風扇同冷氣比佢都係咁<br />\n但係我另外一隻poodle 又冇咁嘅問題<br />\n佢肯食野飲水去廁所  <br />\n所以我想問下咁多位巴打隻狗有冇試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sO9EXXL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsO9EXXL.png&h=1734258e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢依家咁樣望住我 但係條尾係收起左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42272f2be8bf65df032fce6ab56e4d5c86872a2e","tid":1975854,"uid":2455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:08:22.000Z","msg":"有時間就陪佢多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589ca5315e98f299f9b55c3974c87e4281be602d","tid":1975854,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:09:48.000Z","msg":"狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45ca5fa34e939d0b02d24bbdc3ed1ab65889808","tid":1975854,"uid":127118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:09:55.000Z","msg":"有無心臟病問題？<br />\n盡快比醫生檢查下"},{"pid":"fff1272743492ac6b922fa2aa4b85640ab530a38","tid":1975854,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:10:03.000Z","msg":"收埋條尾有咩問題"},{"pid":"b878152c3d4c3f6e35df91b498d5ef045527e750","tid":1975854,"uid":163654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b45ca5fa34e939d0b02d24bbdc3ed1ab65889808","tid":1975854,"uid":127118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:09:55.000Z","msg":"有無心臟病問題？<br />\n盡快比醫生檢查下