>迴光反照</span>咁 好痴人 跟實你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後就詳和地離開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申隻狗養左16年到</blockquote><br />\n關於該現象的科學解釋，一般認為是人體調動免疫和內分泌系統對疾病進行最後抵抗所致。其反應包括<span style=\"color: red;\">大量ATP在短時間內水解為ADP為機體供能</span>，同時下丘腦和垂體促使腎上腺皮質立即分泌大量的腎上腺素和皮質激素，激活交感神經興奮點，<span style=\"color: red;\">使病人回復相對正常的心肌收縮頻率，血液循環加快，大腦、心臟、肺、肝、腎等器官因供血突然趨於正常</span>。"},{"pid":"a1ce694db60a29012e140a11b43d444f01c78f1f","tid":1975854,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:03:56.000Z","msg":"樓豬隻狗一定冇事既 加油"},{"pid":"8bab6c441be3746b23d8400cad55e9e9dd566728","tid":1975854,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b60cdd2d63bc2cf080e88097f170e67b5b9ca0f","tid":1975854,"uid":59522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T23:25:17.000Z","msg":"我隻狗走之前都好癡<br />\n你唔多啲錫佢會後悔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:06:11.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n要及時睇醫生<br />\n要及時愛<br />\n唔係後悔"},{"pid":"c9e8caf3626dbb43ae22c7cfb59dcfc708de9ae7","tid":1975854,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:13:16.000Z","msg":"睇醫生驗血最好驗埋胰臟<br />\n唔好拖 早驗到早醫到<br />\n我隻貴婦今年11歲 <br />\n我直頭想半年幫佢Bodycheck一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a8651f3aa8de283d1287badb696a90048bf3eb","tid":1975854,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:18:50.000Z","msg":"我之前隻狗都試過喘氣<br />\n最後心臟病+肺積水+腹水...<br />\n佢臨走前一晚, 好乖咁陪我睇左一晚波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64d5ceeef93a1789456f42c96eb6539fd9918d4","tid":1975854,"uid":163654,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"醫生話隻衰妹冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vuBi6W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c